Usage: group [-help] <inst|hInst>+ [ [ -module_name <module_name> -hinst_base_name <hinst_base_name> ] ]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
<inst|hInst>+                          # A list of one or more inst/hinst in
                                       # same hierarchy ((inst|hInst)+, required)
-hinst_base_name <hinst_base_name>     # specify hinst base name of new group
                                       # instantiation (string, optional)
-module_name <module_name>             # specify module name of new group
                                       # (string, optional)